        	<h2>About WonderOps</h2>
             <div class="why-cho_inner_subtext"><img src="./images/hat-wand.jpg">

WonderOps services are focused on providing value added information security services to small businesses. As a small business ourself, we know what it is like and how challenging it can be to need to find competent support while managing costs. Our objective is simply to provide good IT services to our clients. Our desire as a company is founded on the belief we can help other small businesses with their technology support needs with skilled and experienced people at a lower cost than they can do it themselves. Every decision we make at WonderOps has that goal in mind. 
<br><br>

The team at WonderOps holds leading edge certifications in Amazon Web Services and Jenkins CI/CD tooling. We have experience in Linux and Windows system administration, Information Security, Enterprise Architecture, Configuration Management tools like Chef, Monitoring, Automation and ITSM. Our decades of experience in the IT industry means you can relax and rely on us to service all of your small business IT needs. 
